About Us
Backbeat Entertainment was founded almost two decades ago by accomplished drummer, Rob Herbert.
Rob has played with the likes of Toby Keith, Jake Owen, Huey Lewis, Tito Nieves, and many others. His keen ear for talent means we represent a diverse array of incredibly gifted, fun-loving artists, who cover just about every style of music.
